
o Update the kernel AIO interfaces to properly set the remaining time
  on the timeout to io_getevents() or update aio_suspend() and
  aio_reap() to use gettimeofday().  The former is preferred.

o When the kernel handles signalling for io completion, add sigevent
  processing to the aiocb->iocb conversion.

o Change aior_getevents() to use the kernel's new wait-many semantics
  for aio_reap()
